<div style="text-align: left;">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">The Learning &amp; Teaching Council is charged with enhancing the quality and scholarship of learning and teaching at BYU-Idaho. This council is comprised of the chairs of four Learning &amp; Teaching Committees and is chaired by the Associate Academic Vice President of Instruction. This council meets at least once each semester to coordinate resources from the Academic Office and the efforts of over twenty-four faculty serving on the various committees noted below:</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><a href="x23098.xml">Best Practices Committee</a><br />Promote best practices through faculty recognition and gatherings</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">&middot;Faculty Awards</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">&middot;Faculty Banquet</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">&middot;Spori Summit<br /><br /></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><a href="x23951.xml" style="font-family: Cambria; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;" title="Dialogue">Dialogue Committee</a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;">Encourage investigation and sharing of faculty research on learning and teaching</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;">&middot;Brown Bag&nbsp;Lunch Discussions&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;">&middot;Faculty Conference<br /><br /></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a class="intLink" href="x23976.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Publication">Publication Committee</a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Publish findings and insights from faculty including conferences, site visits, and research</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;">&middot;Perspectives Magazine<br /><br /></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a class="intLink" href="x24011.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Travel">Travel Committee</a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Coordinate selection and travel for faculty groups while developing cross-disciplinary friendships</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;">&middot;Best Practices site visits</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;">&middot;Teaching Conferences</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"></p>
